Documentation here
https://github.com/Microsoft/vscode-chrome-debug

0. In Code, set some breakpoints
1. Close all instances of Chrome
2. In Terminal, run 'kill Chrome'
3. In Terminal, run the command below

/Applications/Google\ Chrome.app/Contents/MacOS/Google\ Chrome --remote-debugging-port=9222

4. In Code, run the application in Debug using the 'xxx' option
5. In Chrome, click on the 'Window:9222' 
6. In Code, see the breakpoint be hit